00:53:28,380 --> 00:53:29,801
Well, that's a really good question.

948
00:53:29,841 --> 00:53:32,242
We actually talk about it a lot right now.

949
00:53:32,883 --> 00:53:38,246
If we should, for example, have the cosmetic stuff be in

